<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>YelpCamp</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css">
</head>
<body class="d-flex text-center text-white bg-dark">
    <div class="cover-container d-flex w-100 h-100 p-3 mx-auto flex-column">
        <header class="mb-auto">
            <div>
                <h3 class="float-md-start mb-0">YelpCamp</h3>
                <nav class="nav justify-content-center float-md-end">
                    <a href="#" aria-current="page" class="nav-link active">홈</a>
                    <a href="/campgrounds" class="nav-link">캠핑장</a>
                    <% if (!currentUser) { %>
                    <a href="/login" class="nav-link">로그인</a>
                    <a href="/register" class="nav-link">회원가입</a>
                    <% } else { %>
                    <a href="/logout" class="nav-link">로그아웃</a>
                    <% } %>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </header>
        <main class="px-3">
            <h1>YelpCamp</h1>
            <p class="lead">YelpCamp에 오신것을 환영합니다. <br> 얼른 저희의 다양한 캠핑장을 탐험해보세요.<br> 여러분의 캠핑장도 자유롭게 공유해주세요.</p>
            <a href="/campgrounds" class="btn btn-lg btn-secondary font-weight-bold bg-white">캠핑장 보기</a>

        </main>
        <footer class="mt-auto text-white-50">
            <p>&copy; 2024 YelpCamp</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>